name: BCOoLExamples
tagline: The project contains examples of the operators in BCOoL. After compiled, an operators can be used to generate the model of coordination between models. Examples of operators are: synchronized product between Timed Finite State Machine (TFSM), synchronized product between TFSM and Activity diagramas. For further information, go to http://timesquare.inria.fr/BCOoL
body:
# BCOoLExamples
This contains BCOoL examples which includes the specification of a BCOoL operator plus a model. The BCOoL specification can be used to coordinate the example models.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
